{{zh-forms|[[春]][[江]][[水]][[暖]][[鸭]][[先]][[知]]|[[春江水暖鴨先知]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: chūn jiāng shuĭ nuăn yā xiān zhī
===Etymology===
Literally: If the waters of the river are warm, the ducks will be the first to know.
===Proverb===
# Professionals within an industry or profession will be the first to notice a change in circumstances.
